  * Improvements
    * CentOS 7: Supported auto native package install.

==== Ruby/GDK3

  * Improvements
    * CentOS 7: Supported auto native package install.

==== Ruby/GTK3

  * Improvements
    * Made more demos workable.

==== Ruby/WebKit2GTK

  * Improvements
    * Added a sample that uses proxy.

==== Ruby/GtkSourceView3

  * Improvements
    * CentOS 7: Supported auto native package install.

