      [patch by cedlemo]
    * lib and tests follow GI API improvement.
    * test omit on old GTK+.
    * require more newer GTK+ version for (({Gtk::TextView})) test.

==== Ruby/Pango

  * Improvements
    * add tests for (({Pango::Context})).
      [patch by cedlemo]
