    * Windows: Fixed a bug that large number flag value isn't usable.
      [GitHub#538] [Reported by Abby Archer]

==== Ruby/GTK3

  * Improvements
    * Updated tutorials.
      [GitHub#534][GitHub#537] [Patch by cedlemo]

