  * Improvements
    * Reduce needless GBoxed object copy.

==== Ruby/GdkPixbuf2

  * Fixes
    * Fix build error by a typo.

==== Ruby/GtkSourceView2

  * Improvements
    * Support auto RPM install on CentOS 6.

